Steve Franken https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Steve_Franken 0 Stephen Robert "Steve" Franken (May 27, 1932 – August 24, 2012) was an American actor who appeared on screen and television for a half century. He was a second cousin of former United States Senator Al Franken of Minnesota.
